snippet.title: Trillanes accuses Duterte of freeing 8 Chinese 'drug lords'

localized.description:
FALSE CRIME BUSTER? Following his exposé on the alleged hidden wealth of Davao City Mayor Rodrigo Duterte, Senator Antonio Triallanes IV on Sunday pounded the leading presidential candidate for facilitating the release of eight Chinese nationals tagged in illegal drug trade back in 2005.
